22
00:02:45,581 --> 00:02:48,626
It refers to a player's death.

23
00:02:50,211 --> 00:02:52,881
Now, let the game begin.

24
00:03:58,820 --> 00:04:00,698
We played this pretty often as kids.

25
00:04:02,616 --> 00:04:03,659
Do you remember

26
