27
00:04:06,746 --> 00:04:07,830
Cut the crap and--

28
00:04:20,968 --> 00:04:22,220
The secret inspector.

29
00:04:25,348 --> 00:04:27,182
We said, "the secret inspector."

30
00:04:48,954 --> 00:04:51,331
Good rain knows the best time to fall.

31
00:05:01,216 --> 00:05:02,843
