157
00:24:45,942 --> 00:24:48,694
I'm sorry for asking you
to come all the way here.

158
00:24:49,403 --> 00:24:51,489
We wanted to send you a car, but--

159
00:24:51,573 --> 00:24:52,949
Why did you want to see me?

160
00:24:54,742 --> 00:24:55,993
Well, actually…

161
00:24:58,872 --> 00:25:02,917
It's been quite a while since
you deposited your money at our bank,

162
00:25:03,792 --> 00:25:06,003
but we haven't heard from you.

163
00:25:10,342 --> 00:25:11,300
What is there

164
00:25:14,054 --> 00:25:15,471
for me to say?

165
00:25:16,222 --> 00:25:17,223
Pardon?

166
00:25:18,724 --> 00:25:21,353
No, that's not what I mean.

167
00:25:24,230 --> 00:25:28,067
Your money is now
in a regular savings account,

168
00:25:29,236 --> 00:25:31,488
but you get almost no interest
with that account.

169
00:25:32,614 --> 00:25:35,157
And our bank recently began

170
00:25:35,241 --> 00:25:39,828
