for our VIPs like you.

171
00:25:39,913 --> 00:25:42,539
I wanted to tell you about it
and introduce myself to you.

172
00:25:43,375 --> 00:25:45,501
You must be a busy man, but I wanted to…

173
00:25:46,126 --> 00:25:49,088
Goodness. Did I offend you in any way?

174
00:25:51,633 --> 00:25:53,676
May I ask for a favor?

175
00:25:53,759 --> 00:25:55,929
Sure, please do tell.

176
00:25:59,307 --> 00:26:01,726
