189
00:30:05,385 --> 00:30:06,679
Please.

190
00:30:28,992 --> 00:30:30,202
Who…

191
00:30:33,623 --> 00:30:34,915
are you?

192
00:30:45,969 --> 00:30:47,135
That man

193
00:30:47,971 --> 00:30:49,388
over there.

194
00:30:51,682 --> 00:30:53,476
He must be drunk.

195
00:30:54,810 --> 00:30:57,896
He has been there for hours.

196
00:31:00,066 --> 00:31:01,608
He looks like

197
00:31:02,652 --> 00:31:04,194
a homeless man.

198
00:31:04,988 --> 00:31:05,864
Were…

199
00:31:08,700 --> 00:31:11,076
you behind everything?

200
00:31:11,160 --> 00:31:14,705
He'll soon freeze to death
if he stays out there.

201
00:31:16,207 --> 00:31:18,960
But no one is helping him.

202
00:31:19,042 --> 00:31:21,003
Why did you do it?

203
00:31:24,382 --> 00:31:25,924
What would you do?

204
00:31:26,009 --> 00:31:27,218
Answer me!

205
00:31:28,428 --> 00:31:30,555
Why did you do something like that?

206
00:31:32,097 --> 00:31:34,017
Would you stop and help

207
00:31:34,726 --> 00:31:41,566
that smelly, human piece of trash?

208
00:31:41,648 --> 00:31:42,817
Who are you?

209
00:31:44,443 --> 00:31:46,153
Why did you let me live?

210
00:31:46,738 --> 00:31:47,739
Play

211
00:31:48,615 --> 00:31:50,616
another game with me.

212
00:31:52,951 --> 00:31:54,453
If that man…

213
00:31:55,663 --> 00:31:58,124
remains there until midnight,

214
00:31:58,916 --> 00:31:59,875
I win.

215
00:32:01,544 --> 00:32:02,586
If someone…

216
00:32:04,797 --> 00:32:06,507
helps him before then,

217
00:32:07,884 --> 00:32:09,719
you win.

218
00:32:12,012 --> 00:32:13,347
Stop talking nonsense.

219
00:32:15,724 --> 00:32:17,727
I can kill you right this instant.

220
00:32:18,810 --> 00:32:19,979
If you do that,

221
00:32:20,563 --> 00:32:23,607
you'll never get an answer from me.

222
00:32:25,984 --> 00:32:27,903
If you play with me,

223
00:32:28,779 --> 00:32:30,030
I'll answer

224
00:32:30,865 --> 00:32:32,700
your question.

225
00:33:04,523 --> 00:33:05,857
If you lose,

226
00:33:08,027 --> 00:33:10,445
I'll kill you with my own hands.

227
00:33:10,529 --> 00:33:11,655
Then,

228
00:33:12,656 --> 00:33:15,076
what will you wager?

229
00:33:16,160 --> 00:33:17,161
Anything.

230
00:33:20,123 --> 00:33:22,959
You can take everything from me
if you want anyway.

231
00:33:35,805 --> 00:33:37,015
Who…

232
00:33:38,223 --> 00:33:39,474
are you?

233
00:33:39,558 --> 00:33:40,809
I…

234
00:33:42,310 --> 00:33:44,939
make money by lending it.

235
00:33:45,022 --> 00:33:47,191
How easily do you make money…

236
00:33:49,943 --> 00:33:51,778
for you to do something like that?

237
00:33:52,404 --> 00:33:53,614
Money.

238
00:33:54,781 --> 00:33:56,867
You know what making money is like.

239
00:33:58,161 --> 00:34:00,954
Is that something easy?

240
00:34:02,623 --> 00:34:03,708
How much…

241
00:34:05,710 --> 00:34:07,295
is the truth?

242
00:34:08,963 --> 00:34:10,715
And how much is a lie?

243
00:34:13,425 --> 00:34:14,510
Oh Il-nam.

244
00:34:16,054 --> 00:34:18,389
