245
00:34:18,472 --> 00:34:19,556
Yes.

246
00:34:20,266 --> 00:34:21,601
That's my name.

247
00:34:22,393 --> 00:34:23,811
Oh Il-nam.

248
00:34:25,813 --> 00:34:27,398
And it's also true

249
00:34:28,315 --> 00:34:31,985
that there's a tumor inside my head.

250
00:34:33,695 --> 00:34:34,864
Long ago,

251
00:34:35,947 --> 00:34:38,367
I once lived in a house

252
00:34:39,744 --> 00:34:44,081
