to living your old life.

261
00:35:39,971 --> 00:35:42,347
Is it because you feel guilty?

262
00:35:48,563 --> 00:35:49,646
Guilt?

263
00:35:53,025 --> 00:35:55,652
I don't think that's for you to say.

264
00:35:55,735 --> 00:35:57,028
That money

265
00:35:58,072 --> 00:35:59,824
was the reward you got

266
00:36:00,907 --> 00:36:03,161
for your luck and hard work.

267
00:36:03,744 --> 00:36:07,498
You have the right to use it.

268
00:36:08,666 --> 00:36:09,958
Look at me.

269
00:36:12,878 --> 00:36:14,005
Life is…

270
00:36:16,548 --> 00:36:17,550
